{"tid":302432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【民族黨因政治理念不能集會　陳浩天：清晰告訴全世界一國兩制是行不通】","createTime":"2017-06-29T11:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T11:55:04.000Z","uid":92301,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"439ecede644afb0f3ce6398a21e981e1f5b51132","tid":302432,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:19:48.000Z","msg":"香港民族黨召集人陳浩天表示，今日就警方發出「禁止公眾集會通知」提出上訴。他說，從警察方面得到的訊息是，基於香港民族黨政治理念很有可能以後都不能進行公眾活動和集會。他說，當場問警員，是否因為警方認為民族黨政治理念違反基本法，所以日後不論民族黨改變集會地點或人數，都不能進行，警員非常清晰地答「係」。<span style=\"color: red;\">他表示這是完全違憲</span>，在香港主權移交二十年的這一刻，清晰告訴全世界一國兩制是行不通，中國政府是不會遵守基本法。<br />\n<br />\n有片<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1942236482659490&amp;id=1487928594756950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1942236482659490%26id%3D1487928594756950&d=wYcR8OGjEg2myXYcDAheuTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=07196a41\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1942236482659490&amp;id=1487928594756950</a>"},{"pid":"8e1206a60467e56ad17fdeafbbaa4d3aa3db70ac","tid":302432,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0307677715193993dfd910c481b48b938408ce0","tid":302432,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"有無錄音, 如果警方咁答完全係違反政治中立<br />\n都幾難甩身"},{"pid":"b5fa5ddc620be799ec3eedec9e4d37bf9f2dd7ea","tid":302432,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無錄音, 如果警方咁答完全係違反政治中立<br />\n都幾難甩身</blockquote><br />\n明係搞9你地啊<br />\n吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472f7d8ea42c11